{"tid":1838294,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"上水廣場手足可以保釋返屋企過年","createTime":"2020-01-24T03:22:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T03:54:29.000Z","uid":89767,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"246c76fbf6193ee1af3a99eae5993566ed11e41a","tid":1838294,"uid":89767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"#高等法院第一庭 #申請保釋 <br />\n#陳慶偉法官<br />\n<br />\n陳<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n1. 襲警 (違反侵害人身罪條例 第36條)<br />\n2. 抗拒適當執行職責的警員 (違反侵害人身罪條例 第36條)<br />\n3. 搶劫 (違反盜竊罪條例 第10條)<br />\n<br />\n案情：被指於12月28日在上水廣場天橋收傘連同多人離去，警員X上前拘捕被告，遭徒手打心口，警員Y遂以襲警罪名拘捕被告，被告拒捕及逃至上水廣場，其間涉搶去Y的霰彈槍，警員曾警告他放下槍，被告沒理會，並懷疑扣下扳機3次，但未能發射。<br />\n<br />\n法官<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">准予</span></strong></span>申請人保釋<br />\n<br />\n保釋條件如下：<br />\n擔保金 100000<br />\n宵禁 21至06<br />\n禁足 所有集會<br />\n每星期報到3次<br />\n居住在報稱地址<br />\n不得離港<br />\n交出所有旅遊證件"},{"pid":"212126441e6933eea3475530520045d89d0a6426","tid":1838294,"uid":89767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:25:01.000Z","msg":"Source: <a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/3309\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F3309&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JXyZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=f7c855fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/3309</a>"},{"pid":"5bb907302d2fe2c0aaa642938b7a6831cde7ed11","tid":1838294,"uid":205339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:28:09.000Z","msg":"十萬⋯"},{"pid":"b9044757317a7077bc43b23efd736b0696297c30","tid":1838294,"uid":259302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:29:32.000Z","msg":"$100000 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da85a98df9d9fbb87926b02392807a0b05fae83a","tid":1838294,"uid":2656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:30:15.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母一單10萬一單50萬"},{"pid":"c367c544ad370a21a7f9f08d9460d601a0c99cc5","tid":1838294,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:30:41.000Z","msg":"10萬係咪戇鳩"},{"pid":"000fca6ab801880360b4330fcfe3cc6ef9e741aa","tid":1838294,"uid":89767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"雖然擔保金高<br />\n但係起碼可以出一出返嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還押同未審先判根本就無分別<br />\n仲要而家嘅案件每次提堂都押後幾個禮拜<br />\n變相監禁幾個月先"},{"pid":"650e6d950e8e685fa72e056a5d9291b285718804","tid":1838294,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"起碼可以出返黎過到年先"},{"pid":"bc61242970e12d0d0f73826c01209f27749cd4bd","tid":1838294,"uid":80931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T03:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足"}]}